      <title>五角大楼因国防部长奥斯汀缺席而面临压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/pentagon-under-pressure-over-defense-secretary-austin-s-absence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀四天没有通知白宫有关他住院的情况后，美国议员要求五角大楼做出答复，称他们对他缺席的解释不满意。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/pentagon-under-pressure-over-defense-secretary-austin-s-absence</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 00:07:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔的诺博亚在全民投票中寻求引渡和仲裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/ecuador-s-noboa-seeks-extradition-arbitration-in-referendum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据内政部在短信中提供的一份包含问题的文件，厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺博亚还提交了九个额外问题，其中包括有关引渡和仲裁的问题，供宪法法院审查，以便计划举行全民投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/ecuador-s-noboa-seeks-extradition-arbitration-in-referendum</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 23:27:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
