      <title>毒枭越狱后厄瓜多尔诺博阿宣布进入紧急状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/drug-lord-s-escape-adds-to-pressure-on-ecuador-s-new-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔最臭名昭著的毒枭之一越狱，安第斯国家其他监狱再次爆发骚乱后，总统丹尼尔·诺博亚周一宣布进入为期 60 天的紧急状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/drug-lord-s-escape-adds-to-pressure-on-ecuador-s-new-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 17:03:12 GMT</pubDate>
